Constant Isentropic Efficiency Compressor model

Model description

The constant isentropic efficiency model is a simple model based on the definition of the isentropic efficiency.

\[\eta_{is} = \frac{h_{su} - h_{ex, is}}{h_{su} - h_{ex}}\]
